item.title: Music
item.description: SoundCloud Videos Blues Take 13 is a video doing some solo 12-bar. After 13 takes it was whatever. Feel like I could do better with a band, my analog amp and something a little more interesting. Sheet Music Musescore has some nursery rhymes and xmas carols I re-wrote in minor.
